    {
        "content": "<p>Your <code>--adapt</code> argument is inferring the name <code>wasi_preview1_component_adapter</code> as the module to adapt, when in fact it should be <code>wasi_snapshot_preview1</code>. You'll need to pass <code>--adapt foo=bar.wasm</code>if you don't want to change the filename where <code>foo</code> is <code>wasi_snapshot_preview1</code></p>",
